Package: gradeR
Title: Help grade R script assignment submissions!
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Taylor", "Brown", email = "trb5me@virginia.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This is a single function R package that helps grade students' R script assignment submissions. This function finds every .R file in a directory, runs it, and tests variables are what they are expected to be.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.4)
